    <TD id="_ctl4_HtmlHolder" class="Normal"><P>Omens of War is the final nail in the coffin for me.&nbsp; With very little to offer in the way of upgrades of damage spells, pet weapons and AA, I find I&nbsp;no longer have the interest to play the class -- or even the game.&nbsp; Sadly, I had high hopes for Omens ... but the game kept me entertained for 5 years.&nbsp; That's more than any other game I've played.</P>
<P>The site will remain as it is for the time being.&nbsp; I don't plan on updating it and would direct magicians looking for more recent data to visit the mage forum.&nbsp; If you're not sure where to find it, check the links.</P>
<P>Best of luck to those of you that continue to struggle with the Vision...</P>
<P><EM>Nenelar</EM></P></TD>
	</TR></TABLE>

</td></tr></table>

