<TBODY>
<TR>
<TD width="20%"></TD>
<TD width="60%">
<P class=welcome>If you play or are considering playing an EverQuest&#8482; magician, welcome!&nbsp; This site is for you.&nbsp; Here you will&nbsp;find information on playing a magician at all levels.&nbsp; It's my hope that the site improves your understanding and enjoyment of the class.</P>
<P class=welcome>As you read through the site, please remember that EverQuest is a dynamic game.&nbsp; It's possible -- even likely -- that here and there, this site will be out of date.&nbsp; This is true of every EQ site as the game is always changing.&nbsp; If you should find that something here is out of date, please let me know.&nbsp; I'll fix it!&nbsp; If you wish to contribute content, please let me know.&nbsp; I'll add it and give you credit.</P>
<P class=welcome>Again, I hope you find the site useful in playing the magician class.&nbsp; If Zomm had had a reference like this, I'm sure he'd still be alive today...<BR><BR><EM><STRONG>Nenelar Valandur</STRONG></EM><BR>Arch Mage of E'ci<BR><A href="mailto:nenelar@ballio.com">nenelar@ballio.com</A></P></TD>
